-- Record Wine Sales in the U.S., Californian Sales Fall
-- B y   A i n h o a   G o y e n e c h e
-- 2013-04-08T16:52:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-08/record-wine-sales-in-the-u-s-californian-sales-fall-table-.html
Wine sales in the U.S. reached 360.1 million cases
in 2012, a 2.4% increase from a year earlier.  Of the total wine distributed in the U.S., 58% was wine from  California ,
according to the Wine Institute.   NOTE: In million 9 liter cases. Retail value in billion usd.  Source: Wine institute            To contact the reporter on this story:
